%p
  Thank you for submitting your #{@event_proposal.event_category.name.downcase} proposal for
  %em= @event_proposal.title
  at
  = succeed '.' do
    = @event_proposal.convention.name
  We will be in
  touch shortly to discuss this with you.  You can still make changes to your proposal at
  = succeed ',' do
    = link_to edit_proposal_url_for_convention(@event_proposal), edit_proposal_url_for_convention(@event_proposal)
  and any changes you make will be sent to the convention staff.
  - if @proposal_chair_staff_position
    If you have any questions, or if you want to check in on the status
    of this proposal, please reach out to our
    = @proposal_chair_staff_position.name.downcase
    at
    = succeed '.' do
      = mail_to @proposal_chair_staff_position.email
    (Please remember that conventions are staffed with volunteers, and we will not always be
    available immediately.)

%p
  Thanks, and we'll be in touch soon!
